highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Netherlands. “Golden” is the highest at #8.
“I'm a Dog” by Kevin Gates is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Netherlands at #21.
“Baila de Gasolina” by Effe Serieus has been on Viral Songs Netherlands the longest, at 191 days straight.
“ACELERADA” by sma$her and MXZI is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Netherlands, up 15 spots at #55.
